# CW Node Helper — Config & Doctor demo
# Record: vhs assets/tapes/config.tape
Output assets/config.gif
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "SF Mono"
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set Padding 20

Type "cwhelper config" Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "cwhelper config --enable queue" Enter
Sleep 1.5s
Type "cwhelper doctor" Enter
Sleep 3s
